<br>
There is this girl that I have known since I was two that lives 5 hours away from me, we barley knew each other till recently, and now we REALLY REALLY like each other. <br>
<br>
Anyway...we hardly talk...maybe once or twice every month or so....but I found out 2 days ago that her mom evidently on a whim left her dad and went off with another guy.<br>
<br>
I have tried calling her two days in a row to no avail(no one was home) <br>
<br>
But when I do get ahold of her, what should I say? <br>
I don't think she has many other people she talks too much, and I don't know how i'm supposed to help her throught this, or even if I am supposed too. I have no idea what to do....anyone have any suggestions.... <p><a href="http://pub57.ezboard.com/bchristianotaku">
